---
title: Creamy Alfredo-Style Jumbo Shrimp and Scallops Linguine with Bacon and Peas
description: What could be better than rich, creamy Alfredo linguine?! We've combined all the classic elements of this pasta favourite with juicy shrimp, salty bacon, tender scallops, spinach and bright green peas for a colourful and deliciously decadent dinner. Buon appetito!
